            <p class="text-[14px] text-[#7a7a7a] dark:text-[#cccccc] mt-2 leading-relaxed">
              经济类相关本科毕业，兴趣爱好涉猎广泛。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-[18px] border border-[#e0e0e0] dark:border-white/10 bg-white dark:bg-[#272729]">
          <div class="p-5 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-[#e5e5e7] text-[#7a7a7a] dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-[#cccccc] flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-semibold mb-3"
            >
              墨
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-[17px] text-[#1d1d1f] dark:text-white">七月颜子墨</h4>
            <span class="text-[#7a7a7a] dark:text-[#cccccc] text-[14px]">国际科技交流语言学习社</span>
            <p class="text-[14px] text-[#7a7a7a] dark:text-[#cccccc] mt-2 leading-relaxed">汉语言文学专业出身</p>
            <p class="text-[14px] text-[#0066cc]/80 dark:text-[#2997ff]/80 mt-1 italic">"梦想：当哲学家和数学家"</p>
            <p class="text-[14px] text-[#0066cc]/70 dark:text-[#2997ff]/70 mt-1">—— 随风漂泊到远方。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-[18px] border border-[#e0e0e0] dark:border-white/10 bg-white dark:bg-[#272729]">
