            >
              便
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-[17px] text-[#1d1d1f] dark:text-white">七月随便</h4>
            <span class="text-[#7a7a7a] dark:text-[#cccccc] text-[14px]">兴趣-棋牌社</span>
